{"tid":2020014,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"新蒲崗 3年大升92%","createTime":"2020-05-16T16:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T02:12:17.000Z","uid":73269,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"45b37e0fb49d19f22dec89a95f14745ea9c293b1","tid":2020014,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"三年前以六折開售的首個「綠置居」項目新蒲崗景泰苑，再度錄得二手成交。物業一個三房單位剛以548萬元沽出，銀碼創下該物業歷史新高紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n房委會三年前出售的綠置居項目，業主於購入後第3至5年，可以出售予綠表買家，近日市場陸續錄得成交。金匯地產密雪英表示，屋苑中層15室一個實用面積493方呎三房單位，業主剛以548萬元售出，呎價11,116元，成交價創屋苑新高。原業主於2017年以285萬元未補地價購入，持貨滿三年，轉手賬面賺263萬元，升幅達92%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200515/MUVLBC7IDXJV7FCTIFMZBMRALQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200515%2FMUVLBC7IDXJV7FCTIFMZBMRALQ%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=63d84fe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200515%2FMUVLBC7IDXJV7FCTIFMZBMRALQ%2F&h=160af896\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200515/MUVLBC7IDXJV7FCTIFMZBMRALQ/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/CrUMB6ice0ijJ3CyH-weR4SomJw=/802x534/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OPKUEMLXA7ULGIK3FDSKDMXE6Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FCrUMB6ice0ijJ3CyH-weR4SomJw%3D%2F802x534%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOPKUEMLXA7ULGIK3FDSKDMXE6Q.jpg&h=df36c5a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7d27d9ae7d57b5171bb219fa2293600d4f8f973","tid":2020014,"uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lOu7GpnaVtg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlOu7GpnaVtg&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xmJq4DTS581XL85RX03p